name: Crypto Turnips
description:
Harvested from the Great Crypto Forests in sectors 1 and 3 of Smorgopovia. The bounty of The Great Flat Disc represents freedom from The Man. Slowly replacing the antiquated fiat currencies of the olde world. Allowing for more direct and decentralized global trade. Having value not controlled by small-minded, greedy humans, Crypto Turnips are the future.
7680 x 4320px  Genesis piece for the Legend of Smorgopovia.
